products.title: Intel Core i9-9900K Desktop Processor 8 Cores up to 5.0GHz Unlocked LGA1151 300 Series 95W (BX806849900K)
features: Compatible with Intel 300 Series chipset based motherboards
Supports Intel Optane Memory, no thermal solution included
products.description: 9th Gen Intel Core i9-9900K unlocked desktop processor. Features Intel Turbo Boost Technology 2.0 and offers Pro-level performance for gaming, creating, and overclocking. Thermal solution NOT included in the box. ONLY compatible with 300 series chipset based motherboard. 95W. Processor Base Frequency 3.60 GHz and Max Turbo Frequency 5.00 GHz. The Maximum Memory Bandwidth of this processor is 41.6 GB/s.
